Quickstrike:






Quickstrike slowed down to a stop, panting heavily. He wasn't a bot for 
speed or that much endurance. He could follow a bot for miles following 
their tracks and their signatures, but running after them wasn't such a good 
idea. He was just too worried that Stingtra would just get herself into 
trouble again. Then it would be his hide Megatron would have.

He coughed and looked around, searching for the sight of Stingtra. He knew 
she was around, sensing her signature near-by.

"Stingtra?" A part of him told him go back to the cave and leave her the 
Inferno alone. If she choose to hurt herself, it was her fault.

But he had a thing for females.
